        "product_description": {
            "value": "The ASR Outdoor Universal Fit Survival Belt combines everyday function with outdoor readiness in a rugged, versatile design. Handwoven from durable black 550 paracord, this belt measures 52 inches in total length and features a heavy-duty stainless steel buckle built to withstand daily wear and demanding conditions. Designed as a true one-size-fits-all belt, it adapts easily to any waist. There are no pre-made belt holes, so you simply push the buckle clasp through the paracord weave wherever it fits most comfortably, giving you a custom, secure fit every time. Any extra length can be conveniently tucked within your belt loops or cut to size, then singed at the ends to prevent fraying. Beyond its comfort and adjustability, this belt offers a practical survival advantage. The woven paracord construction means you have a supply of strong, reliable cordage available whenever you need it, making it ideal for camping, hiking, hunting, emergency preparedness, and general outdoor use. The classic black color pairs well with casual and tactical outfits alike, while the corrosion-resistant stainless steel buckle keeps the belt looking sharp for years. Whether you are heading into the backcountry or just want a dependable everyday belt with an added layer of utility, the ASR Outdoor Survival Paracord Belt delivers comfort, adjustability, and peace of mind in one tough package.",
